  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 72.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was not the only thing different about Dora.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dora was also different in other terms, in that what we had been doing in Dora.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were to assemble V weapons, the V-1 and V-2, and also began to work on the V-3.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These were the first [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] wonder weapons that Germany promised the nation, from which they believed the war will change.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were the weapons that destroyed a lot of London and other British towns in 1944 and 1945.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The head engineer of these missiles was no other but Wernher von Braun, the same Wernher von Braun who started up our rocket program in the United States.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he brought with him, when he was brought to the United States, the entire Dora crew, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] some of whom have been deported by now from the United States.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We had a good inkling of what was going on because the Allies were flying overhead, and there was no longer any defense.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were no longer any German [GERMAN] or any German fighters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were just ruling the skies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this cooled our hearts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We looked up and looked at one another and thought, maybe this is it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Maybe we will be liberated here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In time, we heard that the front not very far from us, we heard fighting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We heard shells bursting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We heard guns.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We heard-- and we hoped that maybe next day, we will be free.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But that was not to be, again.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
